text: Basundhara Humagain (Nepali: बसुन्धरा हुमागाईं) is Nepalese politician and member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly and he was elected from Kavrepalanchok 2 (B) for the Nepali Congress. He had previously serving as Minister for Agriculture and Livestock Development of Bagmati Province in Rajendra Pandey cabinet. == References == Category:Year of birth missing Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Basundhara Humagain
